## Translations (All Rights Reserved)

Copyright (c) 2026 Christopher G. Zuger. All rights reserved.

The following original creative works contained in this repository
are protected by copyright:

- The **Latin-script Croatian transliterations** (shorthand and
  expanded forms) of the Voynich Manuscript text. The original
  manuscript is written in Glagolitic script, which is in the public
  domain. The rendering of that Glagolitic into Latin-script Croatian,
  including all interpretive choices in shorthand expansion and word
  reconstruction, is original work.
- The **English translations** of the Voynich Manuscript text.

This includes all files in:

- `translations/` (all subdirectories and files)
- `papers/voynich_croatian_complete.pdf`
- `papers/voynich_croatian_review.pdf`
- All interlinear translation content (Croatian Latin-script and English layers)
- All recipe extraction text (Croatian and English)
- The RECIPE_INDEX.md recipe descriptions

The original manuscript (Beinecke MS 408) is in the public domain.
The Glagolitic script content of the manuscript is in the public domain.
The character mapping, decipherment methodology, and statistical analysis
are released under the MIT License above.

The Latin-script Croatian transliterations and English translations
may not be reproduced, distributed, or used commercially without
written permission from the copyright holder.

For licensing inquiries: Open a GitHub issue or contact via the repository.

## Manuscript Images

All folio images are from the Yale University Beinecke Rare Book & Manuscript
Library digital collection of MS 408, accessed via IIIF. The manuscript is
pre-1500 and in the public domain.
